339/post/900016490.html |title="Juno" wins in Rome |author=Morfoot, Addie |date=2007-10-28 |publisher=Variety |accessdate=2013-05-23 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cinemastlouis.org/fest.html |title=16th Annual AT&T St. Louis International Film Festival: Festival Highlights |date=2007-11-22 |publisher=Cinema St Louis |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080303042041/http://www.cinemastlouis.org/fest.html |archivedate=2008-03-03 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2013-03-16 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.stockholmfilmfestival.se/en/festival/2007/vinnare/ |title=Stockholm Festival Winners 2007 |publisher=Stockholm International Film Festival |accessdate=2012-02-16 |archivedate=2012-02-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120216171342/http://www.stockholmfilmfestival.se/en/festival/2007/vinnare/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.psfilmfest.org/news/detail.aspx?NID=119&year=2007 |title=Juno To Receive Chairman’s Vanguard Award at 19th Annual Palm Springs International Film Festival Awards Gala |date=2007-11-08 |publisher=Palm Springs International Film Festival |accessdate=2013-11-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120215082939/http://www.psfilmfest.org/news/detail.aspx?NID=119&year=2007 |archivedate=2012-02-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

