eurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121105034428/http://www.canada.com/theprovince/news/etoday/story.html?id=9d359a06-5dda-4898-9f84-c98f5dfc8d49 |archivedate=2012-11-05 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。影片上映一个月后，这种电话的销量暴增了759%<ref name=theprovince/>，并且成为《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》推荐的“送给影迷的十个最酷礼物”之一<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0,,20165615,00.html |title=10 Cool Gifts for Film Buffs |publisher=Entertainment Weekly |accessdate=2013-11-01 |archivedate=2013-10-21 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131021204012/http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0%2C%2C20165615%2C00.html }}</ref>。

